# This probably can be renamed back to FvwmButtons-Osx or maybe -Defaut later,
# but not until fvwm is changed to accept a delimiter.

DestroyModuleConfig FvwmButtons-OsxCentral: *
*FvwmButtons-OsxCentral: Geometry 263x112+273-0
*FvwmButtons-OsxCentral: Colorset 10
*FvwmButtons-OsxCentral: Frame 1
*FvwmButtons-OsxCentral: Rows 11
*FvwmButtons-OsxCentral: Font -adobe-helvetica-bold-r-*-*-10-*-*-*-*-*-*-*
*FvwmButtons-OsxCentral: (2x10, Swallow  "FvwmPager-Single" "FvwmPager FvwmPager-Single * *")
*FvwmButtons-OsxCentral: (1x5, Swallow "xbiff" `Exec exec xbiff -bg $[bg.cs13] -fg $[fg.cs13]`)
*FvwmButtons-OsxCentral: (1x5, Padding 0 0, Container(Rows 3))
*FvwmButtons-OsxCentral: (2x1, Title Desker, Panel(right, position module bottom mlr mtb) \
	"FvwmPager-Desker" 'Module FvwmPager FvwmPager-Desker 0 3')
*FvwmButtons-OsxCentral: (1x1, Title <-, Action 'Desk -1 0 3')
*FvwmButtons-OsxCentral: (1x1, Title ->, Action 'Desk 1 0 3')
*FvwmButtons-OsxCentral: (1x1, Title <-, Action 'FuncFvwmButtons-OsxCentralPrev')
*FvwmButtons-OsxCentral: (1x1, Title ->, Action 'FuncFvwmButtons-OsxCentralNext')
*FvwmButtons-OsxCentral: (End)
*FvwmButtons-OsxCentral: (2x5, Colorset 13, Swallow(UseOld,NoHints) "xload" \
	`Exec exec xload -bg $[bg.cs13] -fg $[fg.cs13] -hl $[shadow.cs13] \
	-update 5 -nolabel`)
*FvwmButtons-OsxCentral: (4x1, Colorset 11)

DestroyFunc FuncFvwmButtons-OsxCentralPrev
AddToFunc   FuncFvwmButtons-OsxCentralPrev
+ I Prev (CirculateHit) Focus
+ I Prev Focus
+ I Current Raise
+ I All (FvwmButtons-OsxCentral) Raise

DestroyFunc FuncFvwmButtons-OsxCentralNext
AddToFunc   FuncFvwmButtons-OsxCentralNext
+ I Next Focus
+ I Current Raise
+ I All (FvwmButtons-OsxCentral) Raise
